(49, 'ayende', 'The impact of IO_Uring on the overall design is really interesting<p>Because it push you toward everything as async by default<p>I can easily imagine node.js implemented on top of that, for example<p>The move to async in modern languages also supports that very well<p>Note that this has major impact globally, not just for the IO portions of the system<p>In a way, this is function coloring all over again', 32878705, 32879173, '2022-09-17 00:00:00', 0),
