(83, 'Bubble_Pop_22', 'They should have invited the DOJ attorneys too. They were more instrumental to Apple existence than Jobs, Cook or Ive.', 32878527, 32880036, '2022-09-17 00:00:00', 0),
(84, 'globalreset', 'Any correlations in there? It doesn&#x27;t seem that hard to break it down by age, sex etc, compare with other stats and shine some light on it. Is it just population getting old, one of the vaccines having side effects, psychological effect of the war etc.', 32878502, 32879852, '2022-09-17 00:00:00', 0),
