(226, 32578206, 'job', 'mvoodarla', '2022-08-24 00:00:00', 'Sieve (YC W22) Is Building AI Infrastructure for Video', '', 'Our website: <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.sievedata.com&#x2F;\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.sievedata.com&#x2F;</a><p>Hey HN! I&#x27;m one of the founders of a startup called Sieve, and at a high level we&#x27;re building ML infrastructure focused on video data. Think about it as something similar to Databricks or what Tesla&#x27;s ML data engine looks like internally, but focused on video and built for software engineers and data scientists who may not know the ins and outs of deep learning and infrastructure. We&#x27;re a team of recent Cal grads with experience at many ML companies (Scale AI, NVIDIA, Niantic, Microsoft) and within a year, have multiple large paying customers.<p>Video is becoming a huge thing with apps like TikTok and Zoom taking over, and smart cameras being installed everywhere from homes, to farms, fleets, warehouses, retail stores, and more. We think we have the potential to position ourselves as the company that brings ML infrastructure to the masses of software companies just getting started on their journeys.<p>We&#x27;re currently building out our founding team.', 0, '', NULL),
(227, 32575785, 'job', 'davidchl', '2022-08-24 00:00:00', 'GoGoGrandparent (YC S16) is hiring a lead full-stack engineer', '', 'About us:\nWe&#x27;re a digital caregiver that helps older &amp; disabled adults avoid retirement communities and age well in their own homes. We tailor on demand APIs from companies like Uber and Instacart to the needs of people living with cognitive, visual, mobility and dexterity impairments. We&#x27;re operating profitably with millions in revenue and growing quickly. Our company is remote first. Total engineering headcount, including this position, is eight.<p>The position:\nFULLY REMOTE | Full-time | US, UK, or able to work 4+ hours overlap with mainland US<p>Lead the engineering as the first Tech Lead (full-stack) at the rarest of things - a Silicon Valley startup that is both wholesome AND profitable. We are also looking for a Senior Backend Engineer.<p>Tech stack (<i>required): Back-end heavy (Node</i>, Typescript<i>, MySQL</i>, REST*+GraphQL), front-end (Vue), deploy (AWS, Docker&#x2F;K8s)<p>Minimum 6 years software experience (4+ using Node). If full-stack, you must be strongest on the backend.<p>2-stage interview process.<p>If you want to help older adults and people with disabilities, send your LinkedIn&#x2F;CV to william@gogograndparent.com (keep it brief) or apply at <a href=\"https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.ycombinator.com&#x2F;companies&#x2F;gogograndparent&#x2F;jobs\" rel=\"nofollow\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.ycombinator.com&#x2F;companies&#x2F;gogograndparent&#x2F;jobs</a> (UK jobs can be applied for from anywhere and salary ranges can be adjusted for location&#x2F;the right candidate)', 0, '', NULL),
